name: Frida Punk 020 - Frida Dolittle
description: Fun fact: Frida was a lover of exotic pets. They were well known as her favourite type of company in lonely hours. Her furry friends were often featured in her work. She is said to have owned spider monkeys, a fawn, an Amazon parrot, an eagle, macaws, parakeets, hens, sparrows, and a rare breed of hairless dog, with lineage traceable back to the Aztecs, called a Mexican ixquintle.
